1) Strong load: 4-way concurrency per backend (recommended)

This is “strong” on T4 without immediately queueing forever.

Terminal A: Mistral (backend-a)
export URL_A="http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions"
export MODEL_A="TheBloke/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2-AWQ"

for w in 1 2 3 4; do
  (
    for i in $(seq 1 240); do
      curl -s "$URL_A" \
        -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
        -d "{
          \"model\":\"$MODEL_A\",
          \"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Write 3 bullet points on Kubernetes GPU scheduling.\"}],
          \"max_tokens\":256,
          \"temperature\":0.2
        }" > /dev/null
    done
  ) &
done
wait

Terminal B: Llama (backend-b)
export URL_B="http://localhost:8001/v1/chat/completions"
export MODEL_B="hugging-quants/Meta-Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct-AWQ-INT4"

for w in 1 2 3 4; do
  (
    for i in $(seq 1 240); do
      curl -s "$URL_B" \
        -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
        -d "{
          \"model\":\"$MODEL_B\",
          \"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Write 3 bullet points on Kubernetes GPU scheduling.\"}],
          \"max_tokens\":256,
          \"temperature\":0.2
        }" > /dev/null
    done
  ) &
done
wait


This runs ~4 concurrent request streams per backend, output length 256 tokens → good decode pressure → GPU util rises.

2) If GPU util is still <50% → step up

Increase concurrency to 6 per backend:

Change:

for w in 1 2 3 4; do


to:

for w in 1 2 3 4 5 6; do

3) If TTFT p99 explodes / queue grows → step down

Drop to 3 workers per backend, or reduce output to 192:

workers: 1 2 3

max_tokens: 192

4) What to watch live (Grafana)

Set time range: Last 5 minutes, refresh 5s.

GPU (DCGM)

avg(DCGM_FI_DEV_GPU_UTIL) → should climb toward 50–80

power rises with it

vLLM

vllm:num_requests_waiting should not runaway forever

TTFT p95/p99 should move but remain interpretable

5) “Strong snapshot” capture checklist

While load is running:

Open Dashboard C (Correlation)

Wait 60–90 seconds to stabilize

Share → Snapshot with data (best proof)

Screenshot the dashboard too (simple artifact)
